                     <title key="work_11568">Distinctiones</title>
                     <note>A series of <foreign rend="italic">distinctiones</foreign>, those on the recto perhaps for the parts of sermons, on the verso for most of <persName key="person_100184667" role="aut">Gregory the Great</persName>’s ‘parts’ of the Seven Deadly Sins, <title>Moralia</title> 31.45.88 (<title>PL</title> 76:621), ed. Mark Adriaen, <title>CC</title> 143, 3 vols (1979–85), 1610.</note>
