                  </msItem>
                  <msItem n="2">
                     <locus> Fol. 2<hi rend="superscript">rv</hi>
                     </locus>
                     <title key="work_15283" type="desc">Theological notes</title>
                     <note>Beginning with materials on ‘elacio’, angels and men as Gods creations, three things which nourish the root of humility, etc., including further <foreign rend="italic">distinctiones</foreign>. </note>
                     <note>Leaves from a priest’s notebook. </note>
